Miss?

7
00:00:45,337 --> 00:00:47,714
Miss!

8
00:00:51,677 --> 00:00:53,512
Good morning. You've reached Tokyo.

9
00:00:54,638 --> 00:00:56,056
Thank you.

10
00:01:00,435 --> 00:01:03,814
I had to get off at Shinagawa
and take the blue line...

11
00:01:05,023 --> 00:01:06,691
but I came all the way to Tokyo.

12
00:01:06,858 --> 00:01:10,696
Um, blue...

13
00:01:11,863 --> 00:01:14,408
Well, there's light blue and indigo.

14
00:01:16,118 --> 00:01:25,961
Bound for Kamata and Kannai...

15
00:01:26,128 --> 00:01:30,549
Get your grilled eel bento,
katsu sandwich, and katsu curry here!

16
00:01:30,715 --> 00:01:32,634
Grilled eel, katsu sandwich...

17
00:01:32,801 --> 00:01:35,345
Grilled eel, katsu sandwich,
and katsu curry...

18
00:01:35,512 --> 00:01:37,055
Grilled eel, katsu sandwich...

19
00:01:37,222 --> 00:01:40,183
Grilled eel, katsu sandwich,
and katsu curry...

20
00:01:40,892 --> 00:01:42,978
Whoa.

21
00:01:46,690 --> 00:01:48,317
Um...

22
00:01:49,276 --> 00:01:52,029
Yokohama...

23
00:01:56,658 --> 00:02:01,496
In March, at the age of 17,
I moved to Tokyo.

24
00:02:02,247 --> 00:02:03,790
Because I hate to lose.

25
00:02:03,957 --> 00:02:05,334
Because I wasn't wrong.

26
00:02:11,173 --> 00:02:12,591
Snow!

27
00:02:21,058 --> 00:02:24,019
This unfinished beat covers the night

28
00:02:24,186 --> 00:02:26,897
Embracing us before we're crushed

29
00:02:27,064 --> 00:02:31,610
Even if your hand is unreliable
That is your own hand

30
00:02:31,776 --> 00:02:34,446
There will be change
If you just reach out

31
00:02:40,243 --> 00:02:44,206
Crying in a crowd with a voiceless voice

32
00:02:44,373 --> 00:02:48,460
Come morning
The footsteps drown out the voice

33
00:02:48,627 --> 00:02:52,589
No matter how much time passes
It never dries

34
00:02:52,756 --> 00:02:57,177
The cold, muddy waters of a decaying city

35
00:02:57,344 --> 00:02:58,679
In a world where nothing changes

36
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:01,514
We have to live through it

37
00:03:02,683 --> 00:03:04,810
It may be dumb, but we have no choice

38
00:03:04,976 --> 00:03:07,562
We've already started walking

39
00:03:07,729 --> 00:03:10,732
It may seem unreal
It may seem stupid

40
00:03:10,899 --> 00:03:13,526
This hopeless city of ours

41
00:03:13,694 --> 00:03:15,821
But I still saw it with my own eyes

42
00:03:15,987 --> 00:03:18,698
I touched it with these hands
See? See?

43
00:03:18,865 --> 00:03:21,993
See? There it goes again
It's so stupid

44
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:24,830
Shine a light through
The hopeless darkness

45
00:03:24,996 --> 00:03:26,998
This isn't a dream
Even in a dead city

46
00:03:27,165 --> 00:03:30,043
Giving up won't change anything
Even now, now

47
00:03:30,210 --> 00:03:33,547
Now, this unfinished beat covers the night

48
00:03:33,714 --> 00:03:36,383
Embracing us before we're crushed

49
